            <title>[LUDOC-296] Rearange presentation to be more top-down</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-296</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The current presentation has the data types and structure definitions first, the RPCs second, and the semantic operations third. We&apos;d like to reverse this order. The discussion of general topics (LDLM, connection, etc.) will still come first.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
